    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/566440/extras/bffc271db481e3ba081c36698f13b74c.poster.avif?t=1695820234\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/566440/extras/bffc271db481e3ba081c36698f13b74c.webm?t=1695820234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/566440/extras/bffc271db481e3ba081c36698f13b74c.mp4?t=1695820234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/566440/extras/dbf063345e0d6afab4f127680f7b2689.webp?t=1695820234\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br><br>污秽不堪、噩梦般的涅克洛蒙达——蜂巢之都的深处，在下巢那些黑暗曲折、令人晕眩的隧道中，势不两立的帮派势力打打杀杀，争夺个人权力、财富、生存权和荣耀。只有最强的一方才能生存下去。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/566440/extras/8630895e885eea85ea8b1510d8b5f8da.webp?t=1695820234\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br><br>引领埃舍尔、歌利亚和奥洛克帮派，对其进行定制，不断助其壮大和发展。指定每一名成员的责任，将他们派到危险的反乌托邦环境中战斗。在战术火拼中充分利用地形：爬上高处的走道获得优势，设置陷阱，伏击敌人，强迫他们与己方进行血腥的近战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/566440/extras/0d877a3fa82386f8676714a9314c9aa5.webp?t=1695820234\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br><br>学习新技能，搜刮设备，带领升级后的帮派参加4人在线帮派战斗。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在竞争激烈的战术RPG中壮大己方帮派<br></li><li>体验内容丰富的下巢剧情任务<br></li><li>沉浸式体验，多种游戏模式可选<br></li><li>改编自《Warhammer 40,000》最著名的蜂巢世界——神话桌上游戏《Necromunda》的首款电子游戏<br></li><li>单人游戏或加入激动人心的4路在线帮派战斗</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/566440/extras/e706715e26ec7332daa4ba10d5257d5e.poster.avif